## Methodology

- **Sources:** OpenAlex (peer-reviewed) + arXiv (preprints), both filtered to the last 7 days with cardiovascular + CFD + AI keywords
- **Filter:** title/abstract keyword match → Claude Haiku 4.5 relevance score (≥ {{ relevance_threshold }})
- **Classifier:** Claude assigns one of six tiers (A–F) and writes a 2-sentence summary
- **Build tooling:** [`aortacfd-agent/paper_digest`](https://github.com/JieWangnk/aortacfd-agent/tree/main/paper_digest)
- **Published:** every Monday, 09:00 UTC

### What this digest does *not* cover

- **Abstract-only summaries.** Claude reads title + abstract, not the full PDF. Summaries describe what a paper *claims*; they do not replace reading the methods and figures.
- **Research papers only.** We don't surface industry announcements (Siemens, Dassault, ANSYS, Philips product blogs), non-indexed conference talks, GitHub releases of open-source CFD/ML code, or social-media discussion (Twitter/X, LinkedIn).
- **Anglophone bias.** OpenAlex + arXiv skew toward English-language work.

For deeper per-paper analysis, chat with Claude directly with the DOI. For industry news, follow vendor blogs and GitHub trending.

*Found something the digest missed? Open an [issue](https://github.com/JieWangnk/aortacfd-agent/issues) with the DOI.*
